javax.servlet.sip

Interface AttributeStoreListener<T extends AttributeStore>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EventListener

    public interface AttributeStoreListener<T extends AttributeStore>
extends EventListener
    This listener interface can be implemented in order to get notifications of changes to the attribute lists of attribute stores within this SIP servlet application.
    Since:
    2.0
    See Also:
    AttributeStoreBindingEvent, AttributeStore
